Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.40,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:04.49,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}穿越阴霾 来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:10.42,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为守护心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:22.92,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}那一刻 齿轮悄悄转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:35.59,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}将新的命运 带到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.12,0:01:38.60,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}恋心 生根发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:41.38,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}思念 深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:49.29,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}在眼神交汇的瞬间 抛却掩饰与矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:55.26,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}心愿只此一件 拥有坚不可摧的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:02:01.09,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}无论在怎样的试炼中倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:03.50,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:06.65,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}再一次 重新站起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:09.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}请稍带片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:15.89,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}正是你赐予了我 将软弱一刀两断的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:20.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}Justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:36.12,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}静静地 静静地 扮在你身边 化身一阵微风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:43.18,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为把你沮丧的泪水  轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:50.23,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}口袋中 那小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:56.96,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只盼你开怀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}跑吧 跑吧 不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:05.57,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}即使发生不开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.73,0:23:08.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}也要在这条路上继续奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.23,0:23:13.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}前方的地图 早已印在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:17.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}明天是个 happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:25.04,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}奇迹般闪耀的happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 今天也是好天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小鸟们还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:27.12,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,500)}{\blur3}羁绊 -Together-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以精灵契约的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命之食粮啊 净化清泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天起早摸黑真能干啊 来我们家做媳妇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的儿子都过二十了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我家的小儿子才般配
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 利萨？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次来玩吧 外孙女可惦记利萨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.03,0:03:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 到时候打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 安娜阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来啦 利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就拿这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 平日里多亏卢克和利萨的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.16,0:03:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些还怕不够呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太谢谢了 一定会好好利用它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多吃点 快快长大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 能再帮忙打两把锄头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有新人来干活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我会告诉卢克的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完 完全没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.97,0:04:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 早起辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天收成好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.94,0:04:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萝卜是收了几棵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 体力恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上了 吃早饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很香哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克 早上了 吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃要冷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有赶时间的活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 安娜阿姨要打两把锄头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次做的还有多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拿那些给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天打些新东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想给塞西莉打刀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没那个兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真失望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 几时开始为那个蹩脚骑士说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 塞西莉一点都不蹩脚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个又漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸部还很大的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 开始锻造吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨 集中注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该吃午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有话想说就直说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太直了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点回去执行任务如何 骑士阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不当班 再说目的还没达成呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要刀的话 拿钱来就给你打
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我事业有成…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 整天刀啊刀啊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底了解多少？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好研究过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不见外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.88,0:08:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我学识尚浅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想多学习一些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想请教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我刀的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想问的是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“恶魔契约”的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相关知识你也应该略知一二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同于以玉钢为媒介的“祈祷契约”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“恶魔契约”是以人类的血肉为媒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓“恶魔契约”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让空气中的灵体吞噬肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使它恶魔化的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些恶魔最初出现在战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是44年前的瓦尔巴尼尔战争时期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很惨烈的战争哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,献出的肉体当然不会再复原
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲是需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争即是对生命的大量消耗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了末期 不明国籍的恶魔四处游荡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 既然叫恶魔“契约”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有契约所需的条件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是死言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死言？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说死言写在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是指哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里刻有禁忌的咒文
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我和你都有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的心脏上都刻有死言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻有？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西怎么读出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办法有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用祈祷契约进行麻醉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切开胸膛 把死言抄写下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者照着镜子 让本人读出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强行实施恶魔契约
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对外宣称是“自愿”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是人做的事吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以恶魔契约才被禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.15,0:10:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最近发生了两起恶魔出现的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且似乎都和某个男子有关
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣男人…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死不足惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种使用恶魔契约的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 大家快吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能一下吃这么多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾啊 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.81,0:11:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我也吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:34.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天要洗两次吗 太辛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:42.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 想到能帮上卢克的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 利萨 有件事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你只有这件衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这件有三套哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以轮流穿……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 女孩子这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.17,0:12:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔在我们家干活 有觉得辛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.20,0:12:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有让我辛苦过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢坎贝尔家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次都没有感觉辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 茶真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 爱情满杯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事想找你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.84,0:13:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 小姐们也有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 利萨也吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.69,0:13:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满嘴溢香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口感真好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么休息天还专门来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是没有赶时间的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有让利萨过满足的生活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口口声声说什么利萨是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:14:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克{\fnsimhei}·{\r}安斯沃思 你有那种嗜好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有必要和你认真谈一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是亲戚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拣到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你无关
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在这里说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有没有为她提供必要的待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从外表看 利萨也是个花季女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是整日穿着毫不可爱的工作服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有给她足够的时间和待遇打扮自己吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也像今天这样带她出来购物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面用餐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再买点东西送给她!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多替女孩子着想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要被你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知 道 了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉 这个很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来确实很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 塞西莉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.34,0:15:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个香喷喷的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是该那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来去那边的店看看～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该挺合身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上试试就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.93,0:15:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么 要给利萨买衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呀 买吧买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以 对吧 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出钱 快去挑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌人多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒 眼花缭乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选自己喜欢的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了 脑袋里咕噜噜直转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起挑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨 尺寸是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没量过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在就量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微忍耐下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多试几件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是这件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.34,0:16:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们试下一件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看 找到件适合塞西莉的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 偶尔也展现下魅力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向谁展现？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么利萨 接下来是这件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 卢克也太没出息了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然雇人家当助手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.67,0:17:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能受雇就知足了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从没有这样过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 还以为他是个一毛不拔的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么爽快就掏钱出来 有点意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这样不太合适
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概卢克也只是不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个比想象中还笨拙的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.56,0:18:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许想为你做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我觉得他只是反复无常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨这么说的话 或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.22,0:18:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.31,0:18:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 我穿着有点可爱过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.21,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…谢谢为我买衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事办完了吧 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉和阿丽亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没出来过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们应该先出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无非又被食物勾走了 别管她们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.21,0:19:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克这家伙 算是什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也不用特地藏起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲尔说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样能让他们的关系有所进展
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关系啊 但愿能有进展
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.34,0:19:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个很少能买到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用来做料理的话 肯定很…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.65,0:19:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨怎么也不说他几句
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.32,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经忍无可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说要默默关注他们发展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.41,0:20:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的谢谢你为我出钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好爱护这件衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多人啊 我玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过卢克累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 今天天气真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
